=== 发行前 ===
第一个预告片发布后，游戏被评论界批评为过于未来主义<ref>{{cite web|last1=Reilly|first1=By Luke|title=Activision CEO Comments on Divisive Call of Duty: Infinite Warfare Trailer|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/05/06/activision-ceo-comments-on-divisive-call-of-duty-infinite-warfare-trailer|website=IGN|accessdate=2016-05-09|archive-date=2021-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211021180753/https://www.ign.com/articles/2016/05/06/activision-ceo-comments-on-divisive-call-of-duty-infinite-warfare-trailer|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Takahashi|first1=Dean|title=Infinity Ward developers reveal their design decisions for Call of Duty: Infinite Warfare|url=http://venturebeat.com/2016/05/02/infinity-ward-developers-reveal-their-design-decisions-for-call-of-duty-infinite-warfare/|website=VentureBeat|access-date=2016-05-09|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112526/http://venturebeat.com/2016/05/02/infinity-ward-developers-reveal-their-design-decisions-for-call-of-duty-infinite-warfare/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Schreier|first1=Jason|title=People Are Mass-Disliking The Call of Duty: Infinite Warfare Trailer|url=http://kotaku.com/people-are-mass-disliking-the-call-of-duty-infinite-wa-1774722992|website=Kotaku|accessdate=2016-05-09|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701003713/https://kotaku.com/people-are-mass-disliking-the-call-of-duty-infinite-wa-1774722992|dead-url=no}}</ref>，甚至遊戲設計和系統很多重用過去作品的元素，導致毫無新意和陳腔濫調，而且未來科幻的設定違背這遊戲系列專門以第二次世界大戰及現代戰爭為背景的初衷而令玩家覺得反感。加上Activision公司將《[[決勝時刻4：現代戰爭|決勝時刻4：現代戰爭]]》的高清重製版和《決勝時刻：無盡戰爭》合併發售，但多數玩家只希望只購買前者而不想要後者，這行銷策略令玩家感到厭惡，令競爭對手Electronic Arts的《[[戰地風雲1|戰地風雲1]]》備受廣大玩家的吹棒和支持。截至2019年12月13日，预告片在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上获得了超过380万个不喜欢，成为[[最不喜欢的YouTube视频列表|YouTube最不受喜欢影片]]的第八名<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mascarenhas|first1=Hyacinth|title=Battlefield 1 and Infinite Warfare trailers break YouTube like and dislike records|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/battlefield-1-vs-infinite-warfare-debut-trailers-break-youtube-like-dislike-records-1559263|accessdate=2016-05-10|work=International Business Times UK|date=2016-05-10|archive-date=2021-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629070313/https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/battlefield-1-vs-infinite-warfare-debut-trailers-break-youtube-like-dislike-records-1559263|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Koch|first1=Cameron|title=The 'Call Of Duty: Infinite Warfare' Trailer Is Officially The Second-Most Disliked YouTube Video|url=http://www.techtimes.com/articles/159146/20160517/the-call-of-duty-infinite-warfare-trailer-is-officially-the-second-most-disliked-youtube-video.htm|accessdate=2016-05-19|work=Tech Times|date=2016-05-17|archive-date=2016-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605072504/http://www.techtimes.com/articles/159146/20160517/the-call-of-duty-infinite-warfare-trailer-is-officially-the-second-most-disliked-youtube-video.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Lillah|first1=Sarmad|title=Call of Duty: Infinite Warfare's 3M YouTube Dislikes Didn't Change Anything in the Game, Says Activision {{!}} SegmentNext|url=http://segmentnext.com/2016/06/27/infinite-warfares-3m-youtube-dislikes-didnt-change-anything-game-says-activision/|accessdate=2016-06-30|date=2016-06-27|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628154556/http://segmentnext.com/2016/06/27/infinite-warfares-3m-youtube-dislikes-didnt-change-anything-game-says-activision/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 發行後 ===
根據[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的評論，遊戲獲得大多數正面的評價。許多人都稱贊戰役模式的劇情、多樣化的自定義系統和更加流暢且爽快的戰鬥。實際上《無盡戰爭》與《黑色行動3》比較起來是有非常大的進步，不過發售之前的污點則一直存在，其人氣也不如《黑色行動3》。

近年來，有相當多的粉絲跟玩家於《決勝時刻》的官方Youtube留言區表示，對於之前針對這款遊戲給予的負面評價感到後悔、慚愧甚至抱歉（有些人還表示至今仍不解為何會有這麼多負評跟不喜歡），並給予不錯至優秀的評價。且有些粉絲也表示期待無盡戰爭新章的推出。<ref>{{cite web|last1=|title=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EeF3UTkCoxY&t=84s}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=|title=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=osompIOly0Q}}</ref>

自《先進戰爭》以來的每部《決勝時刻》都有需要付費抽獎才能獲得的物品，這些物品大多數都是裝飾用途，但也包括新武器。跟之前的《黑色行動3》與後來因爲此系統受到大量批評的《黑色行動4》相比，《無盡戰爭》在這方面對玩家相當友好，也是《無盡戰爭》評價轉好的原因之一。


